#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.homepage
msgid ""
"<br/>Engaging, meaningful interactions foster community. We prioritize open "
"communication, ensuring alignment with your interests and seamless "
"collaboration throughout your membership journey."
msgstr ""
"<br/>Meningsfulde og interessante interaktioner styrker fællesskabsfølelsen. "
"Vi prioriterer åben kommunikation for at sikre, at dine interesser bliver "
"varetaget, og at samarbejdet forløber problemfrit gennem hele dit medlemskab."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.homepage
