#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.homepage
msgid "<strong>Are partnerships with other clubs approved?</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Er partnerskaber med andre klubber godkendt?</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Audience Segmentation:</strong> Target specific groups—like VIP "
"members or recent joiners—for more personalized outreach."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Målgruppesegmentering:</strong> Henvend dig til bestemte grupper, "
"såsom VIP-medlemmer eller nye medlemmer, for at sende mere personlige "
"beskeder."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Automate Your Renewals</strong><br/>\n"
"                <br/>\n"
"                Set up automatic reminders and renewal workflows in the "
"Subscription app to avoid missed payments and lapses in membership. Combine "
"it with automated email marketing to re-engage members who haven't renewed."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Automatisér dine fornyelser</strong><br/>\n"
"               <br/> \n"
"                Opsæt automatiske påmindelser og fornyelsesworkflows i "
"Subscription-appen for at undgå manglende betalinger og udløb af "
"medlemskaber. Kombinér det med automatiseret e-mailmarketing for at "
"genengagere medlemmer, der ikke har fornyet."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Automated Billing &amp; Invoicing:</strong> Reduce administrative "
"overhead by automating invoicing and payment reminders."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Automatiseret fakturering:</strong> Reducér det administrative "
"arbejde ved at automatisere fakturering og betalingspåmindelser."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Branded Products:</strong> Offer branded items like t-shirts, mugs, "
"or event tickets in your online shop."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Mærkevarer:</strong> Tilbyd mærkevarer som T-shirts, krus eller "
"billetter til arrangementer i din onlinebutik."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Bundle Memberships with Exclusive Products or Events</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Kombinér medlemskaber med eksklusive produkter eller arrangementer</"
"strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>CRM Integration:</strong> Capture new leads directly from event sign-"
"ups and follow up post-event."
msgstr ""
"<strong>CRM-integration:</strong> Indsaml nye leads direkte fra tilmeldinger "
"til begivenheden, og følg op efter arrangementet."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.homepage
msgid "<strong>Can you trust our community partners?</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Kan du stole på vores community-partnere?</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Churn Reduction:</strong> Use metrics and automatic follow-ups to "
"reduce cancellations and boost renewals."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Reduktion af frafald:</strong> Brug målinger og automatiske "
"opfølgninger til at reducere opsigelser og øge fornyelser."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Coupons &amp; Promotions:</strong> Launch exclusive offers and "
"campaigns to drive traffic and sales."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Kuponer og kampagner:</strong> Tilbyd eksklusive tilbud eller "
"kampagner for at øge besøgstallet og salget."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Email Campaigns:</strong> Announce new events, welcome new members, "
"or send newsletters with beautifully designed emails."
msgstr ""
"<strong>E-mailkampagner:</strong> Annoncér nye begivenheder, byd nye "
"medlemmer velkommen, eller send nyhedsbreve med smukt designede e-mails."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Event Management:</strong> Plan and manage seminars, galas, "
"tournaments, or online webinars with ease."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Begivenhedsstyring:</strong> Planlæg og administrér seminarer, "
"gallaer, turneringer eller online-webinarer nemt og enkelt."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Event Pages:</strong> Automatically create sleek event pages with "
"schedules, speaker bios, and registration forms."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Begivenhedssider:</strong> Opret automatisk elegante "
"begivenhedssider med tidsplaner, talerbiografier og tilmeldingsformularer."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Flexible Plans:</strong> Create different subscription models—"
"monthly, annual, family, student, etc."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Fleksible abonnementer:</strong> Opret forskellige "
"abonnementsmodeller — månedligt, årligt, familie, studerende osv."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Follow-Ups and Reminders:</strong> Automate communications for "
"membership expirations, event invitations, and special announcements to keep "
"your community engaged."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Opfølgning og påmindelser:</strong> Automatisér kommunikationen om "
"udløb af medlemskaber, invitationer til arrangementer og særlige meddelelser "
"for at fastholde engagementet i dit fællesskab."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:event.event,description:members_club.event_event_1
msgid "<strong>Free for members | Guests €30</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Gratis for medlemmer | Gæster 30 €</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.homepage
msgid "<strong>How is your privacy protected?</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Hvordan beskyttes dit privatliv?</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Integrated Contact Forms:</strong> Connect your forms directly to "
"your CRM pipeline to follow up with interest."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Integrerede kontaktformularer:</strong> Forbind dine formularer "
"direkte til din CRM-pipeline for at følge op på henvendelser."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.homepage
msgid "<strong>Is the membership process straightforward?</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Er tilmeldingsprocessen ligetil?</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Lead Management:</strong> Track incoming requests, categorize "
"potential members, and nurture them through a personalized onboarding "
"journey."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Lead-administration:</strong> Hold styr på indkommende henvendelser, "
"kategorisér potentielle medlemmer, og guid dem gennem en personlig "
"introduktionsproces."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Marketing Automation:</strong> Trigger actions based on user behavior"
"—for example, follow up with visitors who abandon their subscription cart."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Marketingautomatisering:</strong> Udløs handlinger baseret på "
"brugeradfærd – for eksempel ved at følge op på besøgende, der har forladt "
"deres abonnementskurv."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Member Portal:</strong> Let members log in to view their "
"subscriptions, past orders, and upcoming events."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Medlemsportal:</strong> Lad medlemmerne logge ind for at se deres "
"abonnementer, tidligere ordrer og kommende begivenheder."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Membership Database:</strong> Manage your current members in one "
"place—view statuses, membership levels, renewal dates, and more."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Medlemsdatabase:</strong> Administrér dine nuværende medlemmer ét "
"sted — se status, medlemsniveauer, fornyelsesdatoer og mere."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Memberships in the Shop:</strong> Sell memberships just like products"
"—visitors can sign up and pay online in minutes."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Medlemskaber i butikken:</strong> Sælg medlemskaber ligesom "
"produkter – besøgende kan tilmelde sig og betale online på få minutter."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid ""
"<strong>Next up:</strong> Stay tuned for our <em>Silent Mornings</em> pilot "
"sessions launching in June—quiet co-working, guided journaling, and "
"intentional starts to the day."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Næste punkt:</strong> Hold øje med vores <em>Silent Mornings-</"
"em>pilotsessioner, der lanceres i juni – stille coworking, guidet "
"journalskrivning og en bevidst start på dagen."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Opportunities &amp; Upsells:</strong> Identify and follow up on "
"upselling opportunities such as premium memberships or VIP event passes."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Salgsmuligheder og mersalg:</strong> Identificér og følg op på "
"muligheder for mersalg, såsom premium-medlemskaber eller VIP-billetter til "
"arrangementer."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>SEO &amp; Analytics:</strong> Optimize visibility and track visitor "
"behavior to keep improving."
msgstr ""
"<strong>SEO og analyser:</strong> Optimér synligheden og spor "
"besøgendeadfærd for at blive ved med at forbedre."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:event.event,description:members_club.event_event_1
msgid "<strong>Schedule</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Tidsplan</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Segment Your Community for Better Engagement</strong><br/>\n"
"                <br/>\n"
"                Use tags and filters in the <strong>CRM</strong> and "
"<strong>Email Marketing</strong> apps to segment your members based on "
"interests, membership tier, or activity. This lets you send targeted "
"campaigns and event invitations\n"
"                that feel personal."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Segmentér dit fællesskab for bedre engagement</strong><br/>\n"
"               <br/> \n"
"                Brug tags og filtre i <strong>CRM</strong> og <strong>E-"
"mailmarketingapps</strong> til at segmentere dine medlemmer baseret på "
"interesser, medlemskabsniveau eller aktivitet. Det giver dig mulighed for at "
"sende målrettede kampagner og eventinvitationer,\n"
"                der føles personlige."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Self-Service Portal:</strong> Let members manage their own accounts, "
"upgrade plans, or cancel via your website."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Selvbetjeningsportal:</strong> Lad medlemmerne administrere deres "
"egne konti, opgradere abonnementer eller opsige via din hjemmeside."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Social Media Dashboard:</strong> Schedule posts, track engagement, "
"and manage your platforms in one place."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Dashboard til sociale medier:</strong> Planlæg opslag, spor "
"engagement og administrér dine platforme ét sted."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Ticketing System:</strong> Set up ticket tiers, early bird "
"discounts, and QR-code-based check-ins."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Billetsystem:</strong> Opret billetniveauer, early bird-rabatter og "
"QR-kodebaseret indtjekning."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Tips for success</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Tips til succes</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Track Key Metrics in Real Time</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Spor nøgletal i realtid</strong>"

#. module: members_club
