#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Email Marketing</strong> and <strong>Social Marketing</strong> "
"apps help you stay connected with your community and attract new members"
msgstr ""
"Apps <strong>til e-mailmarketing</strong> og <strong>til Markedsføring på "
"sociale medier</strong> gør det nemt at holde kontakten med dit fællesskab "
"og tiltrække nye medlemmer"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Event App</strong> will help you. build and manage great events "
"for your members."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Arrangementerappen</strong> hjælper dig med at oprette og "
"administrere fantastiske begivenheder for dine medlemmer."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid "The Power of Presence"
msgstr "Kraften i tilstedeværelse"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid ""
"The evening began not with silence, but with laughter, as Leona shared her "
"own struggles with slowing down in a world that celebrates speed. “I used to "
"think productivity was my personality,” she said. “Then I burned out—and "
"found that what I’d been avoiding all along was silence.”"
msgstr ""
"Aftenen begyndte ikke i stilhed, men i latter, da Leona fortalte om sine "
"egne udfordringer med at sænke tempoet i en verden, der hylder hastighed. "
"\"Jeg troede engang, at produktivitet var en del af min personlighed,\" "
"sagde hun. \"Så brændte jeg ud – og opdagede, at det, jeg hele tiden havde "
"undgået, var stilheden.\""

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:event.event,description:members_club.event_event_1
msgid ""
"The evening includes a relaxed fireside chat, audience Q&amp;A, and time to "
"connect with fellow members over drinks."
msgstr ""
"Aftenen byder på en afslappet samtale ved pejsen, spørgsmål fra publikum og "
"god tid til at netværke med andre medlemmer over en drink."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:product.public.category,website_description:members_club.product_public_category_3
msgid "Thoughtful presents for every occasion."
msgstr "Betænksomme gaver til enhver lejlighed."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To manage memberships in the <strong>CRM</strong> app, start by creating the "
"necessary membership levels under the <strong>Configuration</strong> tab."
msgstr ""
"For at administrere medlemskaber i <strong>CRM</strong>-appen skal du først "
"oprette de nødvendige medlemskabsniveauer under fanen <strong>Konfiguration</"
"strong>."

#. module: members_club
#: model:website.menu,name:members_club.website_menu_4
msgid "Top Menu for Website 1"
msgstr "Hovedmenu for hjemmeside 1"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Track attendance at events with the <strong>Events check-in</strong> feature"
msgstr ""
"Spor deltagelse ved begivenheder med indtjekningsfunktionen "
"til<strong>arrangementer</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Upload your membership agreements, waivers, or code of conduct to the "
"<strong>Sign</strong> app. New members can sign digitally—no printing, "
"scanning, or delays—making onboarding seamless and professional.<br/>\n"
"            <br/>"
msgstr ""
"Upload dine medlemsaftaler, ansvarsfraskrivelser eller adfærdskodekser til "
"<strong>e-Signatur</strong>-appen. Nye medlemmer kan underskrive digitalt "
"uden udskrivning, scanning eller forsinkelser, hvilket gør onboarding både "
"problemfri og professionel.<br/>\n"
"            <br/>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use dashboards and reports across <strong>CRM</strong>, <strong>Sales</"
"strong>, and <strong>Subscription</strong> to track critical KPIs like "
"membership growth, churn rate, and event ROI. Make informed decisions faster "
"and\n"
"                optimize what works."
msgstr ""
"Brug dashboards og rapporter i <strong>CRM</strong>, <strong>Salg</strong> "
"og <strong>Abonnementer</strong> til at følge vigtige KPI’er som "
"medlemsvækst, frafaldsprocent og ROI for begivenheder. Træf hurtigere, "
"velinformerede beslutninger og\n"
"                optimer det, der virker."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong>Appointments</strong> app to let prospects or members book "
"consultations or tours"
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong>Aftalerappen</strong> til at lade potentielle kunder eller "
"medlemmer booke konsultationer eller rundvisninger"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the CRM and Membership apps together to build strong relationships with "
"new prospects and existing members."
msgstr ""
"Brug CRM- og medlemskabsappsene sammen til at opbygge stærke relationer med "
"både nye potentielle kunder og eksisterende medlemmer."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Using the <strong>CRM</strong> to manage membership inquiries, partnerships, "
"and onboarding"
msgstr ""
"Brug af <strong>CRM</strong> til at administrere forespørgsler om "
"medlemskab, partnerskaber og onboarding"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Using the <strong>Membership</strong> and <strong>Subscription</strong> apps "
"to track active members and automate renewals"
msgstr ""
"Brug af <strong>Medlemskab-</strong> og <strong>Abonnementerappesene</"
"strong> til at spore aktive medlemmer og automatisere fornyelser"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:product.public.category,website_description:members_club.product_public_category_5
msgid "Valuable tools and guides for personal growth."
msgstr "Værdifulde værktøjer og vejledninger til personlig udvikling."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.homepage
msgid ""
"We collaborate with reputable, high-quality partners to bring you "
"exceptional experiences and services."
msgstr ""
"Vi samarbejder med nøje udvalgte, velrenommerede partnere for at give dig "
"enestående oplevelser og service."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.homepage
msgid ""
"We offer exclusive experiences, ensuring that every member enjoys "
"personalized services tailored to their lifestyle."
msgstr ""
"Vi tilbyder eksklusive oplevelser og sikrer, at hvert medlem nyder "
"personlige tjenester, der er skræddersyet til deres livsstil."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.homepage
msgid ""
"We provide support through various channels, including live chat, email, and "
"phone, to assist with any inquiries regarding your membership."
msgstr ""
"Vi tilbyder support via forskellige kanaler, herunder livechat, e-mail og "
"telefon, for at hjælpe med eventuelle spørgsmål om dit medlemskab."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid ""
"We welcomed mindfulness coach <strong>Leona Vervain</strong>, known for her "
"grounded, no-nonsense approach to meditation and breathwork. With a "
"background in neuroscience and a decade of experience leading retreats "
"across Europe, Leona guided us through a 90-minute session called <em>“The "
"Art of the Pause.”</em>"
msgstr ""
"Vi bød velkommen til mindfulness-coachen <strong>Leona Vervain</strong>, der "
"er kendt for sin jordnære og praktiske tilgang til meditation og "
"åndedrætsøvelser. Med en baggrund i neurovidenskab og ti års erfaring med at "
"lede retreats i hele Europa guidede hun os gennem en 90 minutter lang "
"session med titlen <em>\"The Art of the Pause.\"</em>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid ""
"We’re grateful to Leona for holding such a safe, welcoming space—and to "
"every member who showed up with openness and intention."
msgstr ""
"Vi er taknemmelige for, at Leona skabte et trygt og indbydende rum – og for "
"alle de medlemmer, der deltog med åbenhed og engagement."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid ""
"What followed was a simple yet powerful practice: guided breathing, a short "
"seated meditation, and a few gentle exercises to reconnect with the body. No "
"incense. No awkward chants. Just presence."
msgstr ""
"Det, der fulgte, var en enkel, men virkningsfuld praksis: guidet "
"vejrtrækning, en kort siddende meditation og et par blide øvelser til at "
"genoprette forbindelsen til kroppen. Ingen røgelse. Ingen akavet sang. Bare "
"nærvær."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid ""
"What this evening reminded us is that slowness isn’t laziness—it’s a skill. "
"One we rarely practice, and yet deeply need. In the midst of full calendars "
"and constant noise, it was refreshing to press pause, not just individually, "
"but together."
msgstr ""
"Denne aften mindede os om, at langsomhed ikke er dovenskab – det er en "
"færdighed. En færdighed, vi sjældent øver os i, men som vi alligevel har "
"stort behov for. Midt i fyldte kalendere og konstant støj var det "
"forfriskende at trykke på pauseknappen – ikke kun hver for sig, men sammen."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.homepage
msgid "Where connections flourish"
msgstr "Hvor forbindelser blomstrer"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.homepage
