#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid "woman in white tank top and black leggings doing yoga during daytime"
msgstr "kvinde i hvid tanktop og sorte leggings, der laver yoga om dagen"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid ""
"“I came because I was curious. I left with a new perspective—and three great "
"book recommendations,” said <strong>Marc T.</strong>, a longtime member."
msgstr ""
"\"Jeg kom, fordi jeg var nysgerrig. Jeg gik derfra med et nyt perspektiv – "
"og tre fantastiske boganbefalinger,\" sagde <strong>Marc T.</strong>, et "
"mangeårigt medlem."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid ""
"“I didn’t expect to feel such a shift after only a few breaths,” said member "
"<strong>Sophie L.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"\"Jeg havde ikke forventet at mærke en sådan forandring efter blot et par "
"indåndinger,\" sagde medlemmet <strong>Sophie L.</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid ""
"“It was like someone turned the volume down on my brain. I walked out "
"feeling 10 pounds lighter.”"
msgstr ""
"\"Det var, som om nogen havde skruet ned for lydstyrken i min hjerne. Jeg "
"gik derfra og følte mig 10 kilo lettere.\""

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid ""
"“There was something healing about seeing other people wrestle with the same "
"things I do,” added <strong>Elena M.</strong> “It made me feel less alone.”"
msgstr ""
"\"Der var noget helende ved at se andre mennesker kæmpe med de samme ting "
"som mig,\" tilføjede <strong>Elena M.</strong> \"Det fik mig til at føle mig "
"mindre alene.\""

